  static generateWithRandom(): string {
    // http://stackoverflow.com/a/2117523
    return 'xxxxxxxx-xxxx-4xxx-yxxx-xxxxxxxxxxxx'.replace(/[xy]/g, function(c) {
      let r = (Math.random() * 16) | 0,
        v = c == 'x' ? r : (r & 0x3) | 0x8;
      return v.toString(16);
    });
  }
